➜摩托罗拉 razr 5G 体验：不完美，够精彩
https://www.ifanr.com/1369946?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	8070
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370136" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wejk.jpg" alt="" width="5805" height="3265" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wejk.jpg 5805w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wejk-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wejk-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wejk-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5805px) 100vw, 5805px" /></p>
<p>2004 年摩托罗拉发布刀锋 V3（下文简称 V3）时，我还在读小学。</p>
<p>我依然记得当时我妈把这部手机买回家时，精致的金属质感和绚丽的显示屏，都让我深深的着了迷。尤其是合上盖子时，<strong>那一声「啪」的清脆</strong>，让我觉得这是人间最美妙的声音。当时我还暗暗发誓，长大以后我也要买一台 V3。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369949" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/86-1.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="582" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/86-1.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/86-1-360x205.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/86-1-768x437.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ motorola razr V3</p>
</div>
<p>不过长大之后，折叠样式的手机式微。儿时觉得最丑的直板手机，在大屏趋势下反而成为主流。曾被我视作科技嫁衣的翻盖和滑盖手机，逐渐湮没在历史的洪流里。</p>
<p>或许万物都处于轮回中。自 2019 年，随着三星、华为、联想在折叠屏市场上的发力，折叠手机又回到我们的视野，并且再次代表了新科技的潮头。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369966" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Mate-X-VS-Galaxy-Fold.jpg" alt="" width="2921" height="1907" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Mate-X-VS-Galaxy-Fold.jpg 2921w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Mate-X-VS-Galaxy-Fold-360x235.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Mate-X-VS-Galaxy-Fold-768x501.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Mate-X-VS-Galaxy-Fold-1024x669.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2921px) 100vw, 2921px" /></p>
<p>在这些折叠屏手机中，最让我感到亲切和兴奋的，自然是摩托罗拉 razr。不过第一代存在许多遗憾，最突出的当属不支持 5G。</p>
<p>在三星的 Z Flip 系列更新不久后，razr 也迎来了换代。9 月 10 日，联想在颐和园发布了 motorola razr 刀锋 5G 手机（下称 razr 5G）。和上一代相比，其最大的变化，从名字中就能看得出来——支持 5G 了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369970" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qvbnv.gif" alt="" width="800" height="451" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qvbnv.gif 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qvbnv-360x203.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qvbnv-768x433.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>在拿到手机后，我短暂体验了几天。如果用一句话来概括这部手机，那就是「<strong>不完美，但足够精彩</strong>」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370104" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmb.jpg" alt="" width="5805" height="3870" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmb.jpg 5805w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmb-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmb-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmb-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5805px) 100vw, 5805px" /></p>
<h3>从外到内，情怀拉满</h3>
<p>看着 razr 5G 的包装盒，你会想到什么？</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370105" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06832.jpg" alt="" width="5805" height="3870" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06832.jpg 5805w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06832-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06832-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06832-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5805px) 100vw, 5805px" /></p>
<p>如果你用过或者知道<strong>摩托罗拉 A1200E（明）</strong>，那么你一定对包装盒顶部的元素倍感熟悉。水墨色透明盖板配合金属 Logo，这就是一代神机摩托罗拉「明」的味道。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370106" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhesjhe.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="375" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhesjhe.jpeg 500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhesjhe-360x270.jpeg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲摩托罗拉「明」</p>
</div>
<p>打开皮质包裹的精致外壳，就能看到这部神似 V3 的 razr 5G 了。机身后面还有一个「眼镜盒」，内含说明书、18W 充电器、充电线，以及一副天龙（DENON）定制的 HiFi 耳机。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370107" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmbm.jpg" alt="" width="5805" height="3870" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmbm.jpg 5805w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmbm-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmbm-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bmbm-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5805px) 100vw, 5805px" /></p>
<p>不得不提，这副耳机的音质在随机赠送的耳机阵营里，音质拔尖。并且附带的三种大小的鲨鱼鳍耳撑，可以最大程度地保证佩戴的舒适与牢固。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370108" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hga.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hga.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hga-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hga-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hga-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>razr 5G 的设计语言与 V3 如出一辙，比如经典的小下巴、再如窗口样式的外屏，称它为 V3 的「复刻版」并不过分。</p>
<p>机身表面，由大面积的大猩猩 3D 玻璃覆盖。这种材质给人的感受就是<strong>水润、晶莹</strong>。和 V3 金属的强硬质感相比，razr 5G <strong>少了一份犀利，多了一份圆滑</strong>。这或许也暗含着我们从青涩到成熟的成长之路吧。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370109" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/adksjd.jpg" alt="" width="5805" height="3870" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/adksjd.jpg 5805w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/adksjd-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/adksjd-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/adksjd-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5805px) 100vw, 5805px" /></p>
<p>由于铰链工艺的改变，razr 5G 不能复现当年用 V3「甩狙」的快感。开合变得<strong>斯文、柔缓</strong>，不似当年 V3 的凌厉、干脆。相应的，盒盖声音也由清脆的「啪」，<strong>变为轻柔的「嗒」</strong>。</p>
<p>如果上述变化让你感到失落，那么手机内置的「复古 razr」主题，或许能激起你的情怀，让你不禁惊呼「我好了」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370110" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhghg.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhghg.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhghg-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhghg-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhghg-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>这个界面完美还原了 V3 的操作页面，甚至连正面的转轴都都模拟了出来。你可以在这个页面打开浏览器、通讯录、信息、蓝牙等。就连拨号界面也是当年的味道。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370111" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhbhj.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhbhj.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhbhj-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhbhj-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhbhj-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>不过当你进入更深一层的操作，它就会自动切换到正常的系统界面。也就是说只能对着表层页面「过把瘾」了。</p>
<p>另外，razr 5G 也继承了摩托罗拉经典的手势操作，比如用力切动两次手机，就能自动开关手电筒；快速甩动两次，就能打开相机等，都是记忆中的 moto 味道。</p>
<p>可以看出，联想对当年 V3 用户的心理把握十分精准。无论是包装盒、手机的设计语言，还是内置的甜点功能，<strong>都是在向摩托罗拉过往的明星机型致敬，向当年用户的情怀致敬。</strong></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370113" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06836.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06836.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06836-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06836-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06836-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<h3>情怀之外，实用吗？</h3>
<p>抛开价格谈情怀，都是耍流氓。</p>
<p>razr 5G 高达 12499 元的发售价，注定它只能属于<strong>小众玩物</strong>，满足小部分人的情怀需求。</p>
<p>从产品定位来看，razr 5G 也主打超高端，其与中国电信合作，加入「心系天下」系列。足以看出其主要定位在商务人士。或许摩托罗拉认为，能在当年花八千元买 V3 手机的那批用户，现在的消费能力已然不用担忧。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370114" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wbhw.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wbhw.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wbhw-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wbhw-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wbhw-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>然而这也牵扯出一个问题，<strong>razr 5G 是「韭菜型」产品吗？其实用性如何呢？</strong></p>
<p>对于一台手机来说，我们首先关注的是其硬件配置，因为这会直接影响到日常使用的流畅性。</p>
<p>razr 5G 标配 8+256GB 内存，<strong>搭载高通骁龙 765G 处理器</strong>。可能有部分人看到 7 字打头的处理器，已经自觉「劝退」了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370119" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mnm.jpg" alt="" width="3136" height="2100" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mnm.jpg 3136w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mnm-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mnm-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mnm-1024x686.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3136px) 100vw, 3136px" /></p>
<p>的确，这一配置相比其起过万元的售价，总有种「德不配位」的感觉。尽管 865 芯片的体积比 765G 大，不过隔壁售价相近的三星 Z Flip 5G 却塞进去了，这可能会让 razr 用户感到心理不平衡。</p>
<p>这颗 765G 处理器我们并不陌生，其首发于 Redmi K30 5G，是目前手机中端处理器中的佼佼者。对于<strong>商务人士</strong>来说，这颗芯片自然够用，轻量级应用的打开时间、流畅度等方面，与 865 处理器差异感知不算明显。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370134" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07062.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07062.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07062-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07062-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07062-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲安兔兔跑分结果，仅有 32.3 万分</p>
</div>
<p>在较大体量的游戏上，765G 的表现自然不如 8 系。好在 <strong>「G」系列是专为游戏（Gaming）打造的高性能版本</strong>，玩一玩王者荣耀这类中等体量的游戏也不成问题，游戏全程帧率可以稳定在 60FPS 左右，表现尚可。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370133" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07068.jpg" alt="" width="4733" height="3155" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07068.jpg 4733w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07068-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07068-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07068-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4733px) 100vw, 4733px" /></p>
<p>实际使用中，如果不用大型游戏压榨它，那么性能上其实不用担心。比较突出的问题是，<strong>手机很容易发热</strong>。当然，这也不全是 765G 芯片的问题，还有一部分原因是<strong>手机的内部构造过于严密</strong>，致使散热不佳，即便机身内部已经有大片的散热膜。</p>
<p>提到内部构造，razr 对机身空间的利用已经达到了极致。不夸张地说，<strong>它是目前市面上工业设计最顶尖的手机之一</strong>。<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qNlu5qyd3B4">科技博主 XYZONE</a> 曾对 razr 5G 进行了拆解，可以看到其机身内部，已经被填的「满满当当」，拆解和复原的过程非常繁琐。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370116" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hasghjw.png" alt="" width="1421" height="879" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hasghjw.png 1421w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hasghjw-360x223.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hasghjw-768x475.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hasghjw-1024x633.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1421px) 100vw, 1421px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ razr 5G 的内部元件. 图片来自：XYZONE</p>
</div>
<p>而与它结构相似的上一代 razr（2019 款），iFixit 在拆解时曾表示这是其「<strong>迄今为止拆过的结构最复杂的手机</strong>」。通过其 360 度 X 射线视图可以看出其机身内部的「拥挤」程度。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370117" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/eje.gif" alt="" width="585" height="443" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/eje.gif 585w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/eje-360x273.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ razr 2019 款内部构造. 图片来自：iFixit</p>
</div>
<p>内部空间的极致利用，带来的就是<strong>更加轻薄的机身</strong>。razr 5G 展开时厚度仅有 7.9mm，重为 192g。无论是单手握持还是装在兜里，都不会有明显的负担。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370115" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/vmnbnm.jpg" alt="" width="5805" height="3870" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/vmnbnm.jpg 5805w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/vmnbnm-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/vmnbnm-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/vmnbnm-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5805px) 100vw, 5805px" /></p>
<p>和三星 Galaxy Fold、华为 Mate X 不同的是，razr 使用的是<strong>双动态支架结构</strong>来支撑屏幕开合，用铰链中轴的镂空部分保留屏幕弯折空间。这可能是 razr 最引以为傲的创新，爱范儿在<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/irFp5ceGxDwfPY3dr3FM9A">此前的文章中</a>曾分析过这种技术。</p>
<p>这个创新带来的最大好处，便是<strong>屏幕折痕问题得到改善</strong>。据我所知，razr 5G 应该是目前折叠屏手机中，屏幕折痕最浅的，日常使用完全不会被折痕困扰。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370120" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ghh.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ghh.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ghh-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ghh-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ghh-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>除了折痕，我们在购买折叠屏手机前，更会考虑其铰链的耐用性。据官方介绍，<strong>razr 5G 的「星轨转轴」的翻折寿命可达 20 万次</strong>。即便重度用户每天翻折 200 次，理论上也可以使用两三年。</p>
<p>此外，「星轨」转轴还让 razr 5G 实现了<strong>无缝对折</strong>，合上盖子时能做到严丝合缝，避免沙粒等异物进入内屏。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370121" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bjabjka.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bjabjka.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bjabjka-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bjabjka-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bjabjka-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>razr 5G 高昂的售价，<strong>并非完全为了情怀和极致的工业设计买单</strong>，其使用的 <strong>pOLED 折叠屏</strong>也占据着不小的成本。</p>
<p>这块 6.2 英寸的「带鱼屏」，比例为 21:9，分辨率为 2142&#215;876，支持 P3 广色域。在<a href="https://www.ifanr.com/1303233">之前的文章中</a>，我们曾向大家介绍过普通 OLED 和 pOLED 的区别，后者虽然在抗摔性和可折叠性上比 OLED 要强，但其良品率较低、成本较高，因此目前还未能大规模应用在移动产品上。</p>
<p>这块「瘦长」的屏幕，对于单手握持非常友好，可以毫不费力地单手打字。值得一提的是，razr 5G 搭载了一颗<strong> X 轴线性马达</strong>，打字时的震感反馈非常优秀，温柔且干脆。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370122" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07012.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07012.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07012-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07012-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC07012-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>比内屏有意思的是外屏。这块 2.7 英寸的屏幕并非只让你用来看时间。<strong>razr 5G 的外屏权限是向用户开放的</strong>，意思就是说，你下载的软件几乎都可以在外屏上打开，甚至还能在外屏上玩游戏。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370123" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jweew.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jweew.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jweew-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jweew-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jweew-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>不过体验方面，就没有看上去那么美好了。目前专门适配其外屏的应用较少，比如刷微博时，看一条微博要下滑好几次，微信聊天也只是勉强可用。</p>
<p>在某些场景下，外屏还是非常方便的。比如我用内屏打开高德地图，设置好路线并开启导航，就能通过外屏来查看实时路线；再如在外屏上切换歌曲、查看通知等等。虽然不是强需求，但无疑能为体验加分。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370124" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bvhjnj.jpg" alt="" width="1498" height="1005" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bvhjnj.jpg 1498w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bvhjnj-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bvhjnj-768x515.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bvhjnj-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1498px) 100vw, 1498px" /></p>
<p>受限于小巧的机身，razr 5G 的电池被分为上下两块，<strong>容量合计只有 2800mAh</strong>。当你看到这个容量，你可能会满头问号，「这么小的电池真的能用」？</p>
<p>实际测试中，充满电我使用了将近 <strong>28 个小时</strong>后，电量还剩下 15%。其中亮屏时间长约 4.5 个小时，包含约 2 小时的微博、微信，26 分钟的 B 站视频，14 分钟的游戏等等。剩余的 23 小时为待机。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370125" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/sdh.jpg" alt="" width="1752" height="2142" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/sdh.jpg 1752w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/sdh-360x440.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/sdh-768x939.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/sdh-838x1024.jpg 838w" sizes="(max-width: 1752px) 100vw, 1752px" /></p>
<p>可以说，如果不是重度手机控，razr 5G 的电量完全够用一天。如果你对手机的依赖比较强，还是在包里放一个充电宝比较稳妥。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370126" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hbh.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hbh.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hbh-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hbh-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hbh-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ razr 5G 支持 15W 充电，充满电需 1 小时 50 分钟</p>
</div>
<p>同样因体积而妥协的，还有摄像头。2020 年，单摄像头的新机已经很少见了，而 razr 5G 就是其中之一。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370132" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asgg.jpg" alt="" width="3136" height="2100" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asgg.jpg 3136w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asgg-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asgg-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asgg-1024x686.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3136px) 100vw, 3136px" /></p>
<p>这颗 4800 万像素的摄像头，成像效果虽然不错，但不超群。在明亮的光线下，得益于高像素，细节保留的较好。相机色彩的调教比较浓郁，看上去挺讨喜。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370127" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20200930_162902177.jpg" alt="" width="4000" height="3000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20200930_162902177.jpg 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20200930_162902177-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20200930_162902177-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20200930_162902177-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px" /></p>
<p>不过在暗光环境下，这颗镜头的表现就不尽如人意了，放大看的话，涂抹感有些明显。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370140" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184835963_HDR.jpg" alt="" width="4000" height="3000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184835963_HDR.jpg 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184835963_HDR-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184835963_HDR-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184835963_HDR-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px" /></p>
<p>好在超级夜景模式下，对细节方面会优化，暗场景的表现有所提升，不过似乎有点锐化过度。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370141" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184827095.jpg" alt="" width="4000" height="3000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184827095.jpg 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184827095-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184827095-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IMG_20201001_184827095-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 夜景模式</p>
</div>
<p>而外屏的存在，也让这颗摄像头可以化身为自拍镜头。自拍照片的质量，可以媲美主打自拍的手机了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370128" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06999-1.jpg" alt="" width="8348" height="5798" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06999-1.jpg 8348w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06999-1-360x250.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06999-1-768x533.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC06999-1-1024x711.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 8348px) 100vw, 8348px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 右图比例有后期裁剪</p>
</div>
<p>那么回到这一 Part 的问题上来，razr 5G 是「韭菜型」产品吗？</p>
<p><strong>答案很显然不是</strong>。无论是创新铰链带来的「无折痕」，还是极致的工业设计带来的美感，都赋予了这部手机情怀之外的价值。</p>
<h3>不完美，但够精彩</h3>
<p>尽管 razr 5G 的配置并非当下主流，可它无疑是<strong>当前工艺最精致且构造最复杂的手机之一</strong>。可以说，它不完美，但足够精彩、足够独特。</p>
<p>从设计理念上来看，当前折叠屏手机有两种方向。<strong>一是通过折叠迈向更大的屏幕</strong>，比如三星的 Z Fold 系列和华为 Mate X 系列。<strong>二是通过折叠迈向更小的体积</strong>，代表产品有三星的 Z Flip 系列，以及今天的主角 razr 5G。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370129" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhgnb.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhgnb.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhgnb-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhgnb-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jhgnb-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>哪一种方向更好？这个问题没有标准答案。在性能方面，目前第一种方向下的产品，普遍更强，可能更适合做主力机。而第二种方向下的产品，似乎更精致，更值得做备用机，或者收藏品。</p>
<p>而 razr 5G 作为第二种方向的代表作，可能不那么普通用户作为主力机使用。如果你想体验折叠屏的新奇感且追求便携，或者对摩托罗拉有强烈的情怀，那么 razr 5G 则可以成为你的首要考虑对象。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370130" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asjkwa.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asjkwa.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asjkwa-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asjkwa-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asjkwa-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
<p>如果你要问实用价值，我想这个问题很难回答。毕竟「<strong>用户喜欢就是实用价值</strong>」。</p>
<p>作为功能服从于设计的产品，razr 5G 必定会面临实用至上者的非议。而对于 V3 曾经的一亿多位用户而言，razr 5G 一定是今年最有价值的手机之一。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370131" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asvhsa.jpg" alt="" width="1609" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asvhsa.jpg 1609w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asvhsa-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asvhsa-768x516.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/asvhsa-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1609px) 100vw, 1609px" /></p>
